Entity Summary

# Summary is an AI-generated executive report for a time period within a Space.
# It is produced and updated by Sistema every night.
#
# Daily summaries are new every day.
# Weekly / Monthly / Quarterly / Semiannual / Annual summaries are created
# at the start of their period and updated nightly until the period closes.
#
# The AI analysis reads both structured data (task counts, statuses)
# and the content of manual Notes written during the period.

Schema
  summary_id              UUID          primary key
  space_id                UUID          foreign key → Space
  period_type             PeriodType    required
  period_start            date          required
  period_end              date          required

  # Structured data — computed at generation / update time
  completed_tasks_count   integer       count of Tasks completed in period
  skipped_tasks_count     integer       count of Tasks skipped in period
  autoclosed_tasks_count  integer       count of Tasks autoclosed in period
  in_progress_task_ids    UUID[]        Tasks currently InProgress at time of generation
  upcoming_task_ids       UUID[]        Tasks with start_date in the next 7 days

  # AI-generated content
  ai_executive_summary    text          high-level summary of the period
  ai_delayed_items        text          tasks and activities behind schedule
  ai_attention_items      text          things the user should focus on
  ai_general_analysis     text          patterns, observations, recommendations

  generated_at            datetime      when the Summary was first created
  last_updated_at         datetime      when the Summary was last updated by Sistema

Catalogs
  PeriodType
    daily
    weekly
    monthly
    quarterly
    semiannual
    annual

States
  status    Active | Closed
  # Active  — period is in progress, Sistema updates this Summary every night
  # Closed  — period has ended, Summary is final and will not be updated again
